eventName: Open House & Drinks at BlueYard × Protocol Labs Network Hub
eventDescription: ​Join us at the BlueYard × Protocol Labs Network Hub from 4-6pm on Tuesday February 25 for an Open House (including drinks & light appetizers). We look forward to seeing new and familiar faces as we kick off a week of collaboration and learning with the BlueYard & Protocol Labs networks during ETHDenver 2025.
